3 years ago today @chef.ip took me under his wing and introduced me to the world of a private chef. Together we catered parties all over South Florida; on rooftops, on yachts, even for his celebrity clients. Along the way I was fortunate enough to help with the opening of @perl_restaurant where I served as the garde-manger chef for over a year and got to work closely with his amazing team. Whether we are developing recipes at Perl, or cooking at a clients house I couldn’t ask for a better mentor and chef to work with. 🙌🏻🍽🔪🔥

ALFREDO SAUCE RECIPE: 
•boil 1 box of pasta until aldente
•bring 1 cup of heavy cream to a simmer 
•add in aldente pasta & 1 cup pasta water 
(It is a lot of liquid, but don’t worry)
•add 4 tbsp cold butter, mix very well 
•add 1.5 cups of grated parmigiano-Reggiano (high quality parm)
•mix very very well for a few minutes until the Alfredo sauce reduces, season with a bit of salt if needed. Enjoy ❤️❤️
